metadata.name: Baby Doge 3D #1
metadata.description: Baby Doge Army is a collection of 10,000 adoptable baby doges. A unique digital art collection waiting to be rescued on the Ethereum Blockchain. Each one has been generated then hand-groomed by our team to be fit for adoption. Join us on our mission and have a good time. Having a Baby Doge grants you creative and commercial rights, as well as inclusion in the community, plus feel great knowing your NFT helped make a difference to save dogs in need.
